<http://dx.doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2020.716>
    bibo:endPage "23" ;
    bibo:journal "European Journal of Taxonomy" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2020-09-11" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "716" ;
    dc:creator "Daniels, Savel R.; Bittencourt-Silva, Gabriela B.; Muianga, Vanessa; Bayliss, Julian" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Phylogenetics of the freshwater crab (Potamonautes MacLeay, 1838) fauna from ‘ sky islands’ in Mozambique with the description of a new species (Brachyura: Potamoidea: Potamonautidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028797>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028799>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028801>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028803>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028805>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028807>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028809>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028811> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028797>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. A Bayesian Inference phylogram and divergence time estimation for the three mtDNA loci (12S rRNA +16S rRNA + COI) for the eastern and southern African freshwater crab genus Potamonautes MacLeay, 1838, with outgroups removed. Bootstrap values> 75% are indicated below each node while posterior probability values> 0.95 pP are shown above each node by an asterisk (*). Where no asterisk is present no support for a node was obtained. Blue polygons on branches indicates species present, on Mozambique ‘sky islands’." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028797/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028799>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Potamonautes licoensis sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (CL = 17.55 mm) (SAM C-A091399). A. Entire animal, dorsal aspect. B. Entire animal, ventral aspect. C. Cephalothorax, frontal aspect. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028799/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028801>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Potamonautes licoensis sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (SAM C-A091399). A. Left gonopod 1, anterior view. B. Left gonopod 1, posterior view. C. Left gonopod 2, anterior view. D. Left gonopod 2, posterior view. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028801/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028803>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Potamonautes licoensis sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (SAM C-A091399). A. Major right cheliped. B. Minor left cheliped. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028803/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028805>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. A. Primary rainforest habitat where Potamonautes licoensis sp. nov. occurs. B. Live colour of P. licoensis sp. nov upon collection. Photographs by J. Bayliss." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028805/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028807>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Potamonautes choloensis Chace, 1953 (SAM A46802). A. Entire animal, dorsal aspect. B. Entire animal, ventral aspect. C. Cephalothorax, frontal aspect. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028807/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028809>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Potamonautes choloensis Chace, 1953 (SAM A46802). A. Left gonopod 1, anterior view. B. Left gonopod 1, posterior view. C. Left gonopod 2, anterior view. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028809/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4028811>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Map showing the distribution of all the known and some as yet undescribed freshwater crab species from the ‘sky islands’ of Malawi, Mozambique and Zimbabwe. Two new freshwater species not yet described are listed as undescribed sp. 1 and 2 respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4028811/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

